10 ounce Chicken Cutlets
½ cup Toasted Pearl Couscous
2.25 ounce Roasted Red Peppers
¼ ounce Garlic
2.75 ounce Lacinato Kale
¾ ounce Dates
1 unit Zucchini
2.75 ounce Basil Pistou
1.5 teaspoon Oregano-Garlic Seasoning
Cooking Oil
Olive Oil
Salt
Pepper
1 tablespoon Butter

Please refer to the recipe card for Step 1.